{"tid":1963914,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"攬炒藝術家兄：如果您睇到嘅話，請您入一入黎","createTime":"2020-04-08T12:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T00:40:26.000Z","uid":321709,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"88d47070561738268917e3ec37bb4923fdfa9f42","tid":1963914,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%83%95%E7%95%B6%E5%A6%82%E5%8D%80%E8%AB%BE%E8%BB%92%E1%85%A0%E7%B4%A0%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%B6%E5%A6%82%E6%9D%8E%E4%BC%AF%E7%9B%A7/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2583%2595%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25BB%2592%25E1%2585%25A0%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259D%258E%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E7%259B%25A7%2F%23&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=e52249bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2583%2595%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E8%25BB%2592%25E1%2585%25A0%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259D%258E%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E7%259B%25A7%2F%23&h=9ccd2e4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%83%95%E7%95%B6%E5%A6%82%E5%8D%80%E8%AB%BE%E8%BB%92%E1%85%A0%E7%B4%A0%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%B6%E5%A6%82%E6%9D%8E%E4%BC%AF%E7%9B%A7/#</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔係講笑，尋晚睇到您呢篇文時，我受寵若驚到對手震左個幾鐘。<br />\n<br />\n我其實本來希望先私下向您講句多謝，但係可惜無您直接contact。而從文章細節，好明顯您係連登手足，所以想暫時當連登係PM，同您講句多謝。因爲連登外我遲D會有比較formal嘅文章follow up（都係一大堆客氣説話，再加希望大家合作推聯署同其他Idea，之類之類）<br />\n<br />\n既然您有跟開Po，您亦知道我過5000簽名後，我俾自己第一份任務就係招攬團體/KOL幫忙。您係我即時要招攬嘅首要目標。正如您文章所講，係初選呢件事上我地理念非常接近。而您亦知道我推初選聯署之前係主力推Po講成立新工會，好明顯係因爲您嘅影響。我對您佩服到五體投地，亦知道您有幾大嘅影響力。<br />\n<br />\n想先同您有段對話，先出其他比較Formal嘅post，係因爲一睇到您篇文章時，我第一時間陷入兩難：平常嘅我，會覺得高調處理您嘅稱讚，會好Tasteless；但係講真，我知道今次如果高調回覆您篇文，會對個聯署打支好勁嘅強心針。我甚至會利用您呢篇文去做leverage，睇下我可唔可以R幾個專訪返黎，甘聯署成功嘅機會就大大增加。<br />\n<br />\n希望您睇到呢篇野，會明白我黎緊，嘗試靠您篇文求上位嘅原因，而您唔會因此睇小我。<br />\n<br />\n好希望可以真正同您私下傾幾句，你可以Email 小弟 leebaklou@gmail.com，或者Telegram 小弟 @leebaklou。<br />\n<br />\n最後，都係要加多句，真係好L受寵若驚啊屌！"},{"pid":"8da5efe6843f0c2471646befa1ffd3596a80574a","tid":1963914,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"Pishhh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978d7ae213872dbfec85f1d8df4f84b421f7e579","tid":1963914,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:35:07.000Z","msg":"有興趣睇下上年區選有大白田西區無初選，最後兩個自己友點互𠝹而死。<br />\n<br />\n中降頭的大白田西選區 - 泛民和勇撕殺最後建制漁人得利 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761091</a><br />\n<br />\n有初選就其中一個贏，無初選但兩個都唔棄選最後一齊輸，唔係輸唔夠人，係輸自私，on9 同未來幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\none more 例子：16年立會新西冇協調冚家產<br />\nSource: hk01 <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/41519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F41519&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=7440b048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/41519</a>"},{"pid":"a0a2f6b1c551aa48a9e3840c91d6dd070076384c","tid":1963914,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"話要體制外抗爭果班講到咁撚勁，咁你地幫香港組織到哈馬斯搞獨立運動未？根本反對果班十個有九個都係後面做 KOL 指指點點炸，你地親身落過前線未？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家社會大多數係和理非，你拎 35+ 效果大過勇武以卵擊石好多！你唔拎立會點用權力及特權條例？<br />\n<br />\n點都好，體制內外抗爭係無衝突既。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不應偏廢。香港已經水深火熱之中，仲要鬥應該行邊條路線，根本只要有一絲機會就應該去試去做，先係香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 武力對抗九死一生仲要推人去抗爭，你地先真係含家產人血九大簋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上特別指 henryporter、健吾、熱狗、毓民 呢班含家產，E家香港利益大定你地私怨大，日日掛住起「台」打「大台」？屌晒你地老母。<br />\n<br />\n泛民已經推緊 35+ 後冇五大訴求就永久投反對攬炒政府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 效力大過你上街，我唔否定勇武，但有大局觀都知邊樣先根本打擊到政權。<br />\n<br />\n35+係一個完整方案，但反對果班一個完整方案都冇，淨係話唔得唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入議會會DQ你，但我想講上街黑警都打柒你啦！！又唔講唔應該做？？會DQ就唔去做，咁你不如唔好食飯啦，可能骾親呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要勇武就唔該一齊武裝起義，而唔係企響後面推人去犧牲，咁同林鄭葉劉班含家產推醫護上前線有乜分別？明明同步另一邊可以封關，但偏偏就唔做，E家有35+就講千萬樣野去否定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸唔係輸議席，係輸左個香港，拱手相讓比中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fb1bbaa8aa88ebae7e038b7cad27a83cc432f4","tid":1963914,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"672263de0a10ca6d6908ce5f625f4bf691ce7ab1","tid":1963914,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88d47070561738268917e3ec37bb4923fdfa9f42","tid":1963914,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%83%95%E7%95%B6%E5%A6%82%E5%8D%80%E8%AB%BE%E8%BB%92%E1%85%A0%E7%B4%A0%E4%BA%BA%E7%95%B6%E5%A6%82%E6%9D%8E%E4%BC%AF%E7%9B%A7/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lih